--- SCENARIO: herson asks to confirm a fuzzy guess; a player may re-submit instead of confirming ---
# When fuzzy matching had to guess a name the bot echoes the interpreted list with Confirm / Re-enter
# buttons and clear instructions. Alice confirms the guess as-is. Bob's guess isn't what he meant, so
# instead of tapping Confirm he just sends a fresh corrected list, which replaces the pending one.

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobby herson
bob: /register

--- DM (alice) ---
alice: /leaders
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">
--- DM (bob) ---
bob: /leaders
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">

--- CHAT ---
alice: /start
ambotorix: @alice* @bob* <backlink>
ambotorix:

--- DM (alice) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*
ambotorix: *Tap leaders* <button "*">
alice: 1. lincol 2. curtin 3. montezuma 4. hammurabi          # "lincol" -> guessed Lincoln
ambotorix: *I read your picks as*Press*Confirm*otherwise*4 picks* <button "*">
alice: <press_button "*Confirm*">
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- DM (bob) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*
ambotorix: *Tap leaders* <button "*">
bob: 1. pedr 2. basil 3. theodora 4. laurier                  # "pedr" -> guessed Pedro
ambotorix: *I read your picks as*Press*Confirm*otherwise*4 picks* <button "*">
bob: 1. pedro 2. basil 3. theodora 4. laurier                 # re-submits instead of confirming
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: 📥 All picks are in* <backlink>
ambotorix: <image *resolved*> <backlink>
ambotorix: <status *Status: done*Draft: herson*>
ambotorix:
